## Summary
This documentation details the Behavioral Cohorts API which allows developers to list, export, and upload cohorts in Amplitude, with specific endpoints for getting all cohorts, retrieving a single cohort (through a three-step asynchronous process), and updating cohort membership by adding or removing IDs.

